Spring Boot E-Commerce Application: A Comprehensive Online Shopping Solution

This is a Spring Boot-based e-commerce application built with Spring Boot for the backend and HTML and CSS for the frontend.

The project incorporates unique features such as:

Personalized Pop-Up Screens: These allow for a more tailored shopping experience by personalizing customer interactions.
Smart Product Recommendations: The application includes a feature that displays relevant add-ons based on the product selected. For example, if a customer selects an Apple smartphone, accessories like chargers, cases, and other Apple-compatible items are shown on the following pages.
These features enhance the user experience and make shopping more intuitive and convenient.
